description: YARD PICS COMING FRIDAY. Polished and ready to shine for its new owners, this 2bd, 2ba 1400+ sq.ft condo boasts an array of recent updates from top to bottom. This 2012 home feels brand new with fresh paint throughout, an updated kitchen with refreshed cabinets and new appliances, sanded and stained hardwood floors, and most importantly, a perfectly manicured and newly landscaped PRIVATE, FENCED-IN YARD complete with an over-sized, brand-new patio. Living in Southie = CONVENIENCE! 590 E 3rd is just a moments commute to anywhere in Boston. Whether your are traveling by foot, bike, bus, train (or even plane)! On E 3rd St. you are within waking distance to all of the popular Southie bars and restaurants, with your grocery store and pharmacy and famous Annies Bakery just across the street!
